query:
SELECT 
  id,
  createdAt,
  updatedAt,
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(createdAt) as created_unix,
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(updatedAt) as updated_unix
FROM gestantes 
WHERE email = 'teste@gestantesapp.com'
LIMIT 1;
